* Canonical source
  https://github.com/mlewissmith/rpmquerytools

* Develop on branches per tool:
  wip/rpmwhy - devel for 'rpmwhy' tool
  wip/rpmlsf - devel for 'rpmlsf' tool
  wip/meta - devel for buildconf metafiles:
             README, COMPILING etc

* Integrate branches via 'main' branch
  merge 'wip/XXX' into 'main' (consider squashing)
  merge 'main' into 'wip/YYY'
  Don't merge directly from 'wip/XXX' to 'wip/YYY'

* Commit messages referring to gh issues
  - Subject '[GH-xxx] ...'
  - Autolink commit message <=> issue:
    'GH-xxx' or '#xxx'
  - Autoclose issue:
    'fix[es|ed][:] GH-xxx'
    'close[s|d][:] GH-xxx'
    'resolve[s|d][:] GH-xxx'

* Release checklist on 'main' branch
  [ ] 'meson.build' version
  [ ] 'meson.build' _package_summary
  [ ] 'meson.build' _package_description
  [ ] meson compile .meta
  [ ] git changelog -x -n -t VERSION | git tag VERSION -F-
  [ ] Create github release ; generate release notes
